    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, are you sure? i get these feelings a lot when i'm stressed and usually it just passes after i do some breathing exercises. i dont really want to go to the hospital if i dont have to, it's so expensive and the waiting rooms are awful. can you just tell me if there is something else i can take at home to calm my heart down so i can sleep it off?",
