      "content": "okay okay, i get it. you're being really intense about it. but honestly, i really dont think it's that serious. i just feel super jittery and my heart is racing a bit. i have some propranolol left over from my doctor for my anxiety, would it be okay if i just took a couple of those to settle my heart and see if i feel better? it seems safer than driving to a hospital in this state.",
